In previous reports, the Secret Service was not forthcoming about Tran’s ability to elude them and did not disclose that he reached the back door. 
This is the security that you provide the President of the United States with the number of radical lunatics running around out there? 
This even after the intruder in 2014 was able to get into the house and supposedly changes were made? 
